[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "どうぞ、ちょっと今調合とかで散らかってますけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01523",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "こいつは……すごいな、これがかつて流行った\n錬金術ってやつなのか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01524",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "詳しく見学したい気持ちもあるけど、\n誰もいない今のうちに話しとかないとな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01525",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、はい。その、話したいことがあるというのは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01526",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ。なんせ今回のヤマは命が懸かってる。\n命懸けってのは毎度のことだけど、特にヤバそうだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01527",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だからそっちのみんなを束ねてるレスナだけには\n前言った通り、俺の事情を話しておきたいと思ってね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01528",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "た、束ねてるだなんて……！\n私、そんな大層なことは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01529",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "違うのか？　俺にはみんなが嬢ちゃんを通じて\n繋がっているように見えたんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01530",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ま、違うってんならそれでもいいさ。\n誰かに覚えておいてほしいんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01531",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺はヌルスラ生まれで、タイニーの近所の兄ちゃんだ。\nあいつのことはかわいがってた……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01532",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だけど、俺はある日突然あいつの前から姿を消した。\nそれで、あいつは俺を探すために監察官になったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01533",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "どうして正体を隠すんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01534",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺の手が汚れちまったからさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01535",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺はあの日、「深海教団」という組織に攫われた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01536",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "誘拐ってことですか！？\n「深海教団」って……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01537",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "星ではなく海、深い闇の海を信仰する教団だ。\n普通に暮らしてる人間からしちゃ異端者たちだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01538",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あそこは「海はすべての母」と信奉し、\n定期的に海への感謝として生贄を捧げていたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01539",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺はそこで生贄候補として育てられた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01540",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "…………！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01541",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "色々と教団の手伝いをさせられるんだ。\n役に立たない奴は深淵への生贄に選ばれる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01542",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "汚いこともやらされた。\n……今でもたまに夢に見るくらいだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01543",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "逃げ出そうとしても無理だった。\nいや、途中からは逃げ出そうって気もなくなってたな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01544",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "どうせ最後に海に沈むなら関係ないって、\nヤケになってたのかもしれない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01545",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だが、俺の番が来る前に教団は突如、\n謎の襲撃を受けて壊滅した……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01546",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺は、任務で教団を離れていたから助かった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01547",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "まさか、パルメ族が……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01548",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "今となってはそう思う。当時は、敵対組織か、恨みを\n買った相手からの報復か、そこらが理由だと思ってたが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01549",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "星ではなく、海を信奉する教団……\nパルメ族からしたら、排除すべき存在でしょうから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01550",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だとしたら、あの「管理」野郎どもが、\n俺の命の恩人ってことになる。皮肉な話だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01551",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "とにかく、恩人とはいえあんな危ない奴らに\nタイニーは戦いを挑もうとしている……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01552",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺はタイニーを守りたい。\nだから今回、監察局と手を組むことにしたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01553",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そうだったんですね……\n教えてくれて、ありがとうございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01554",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺個人としてはパルメ族の管理に救われたわけだし、\n感謝しつつも穏便にご勇退を願いたいんだけどね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01555",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "もし、俺が死んだらこの真相をタイニーに伝えるか、\nそれは嬢ちゃんに任せる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01556",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そんな、縁起でもないこと……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01557",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "真実を知ったほうがタイニーのためになるのか……\nその判断を、嬢ちゃんに頼みたいんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01558",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "大丈夫、どんな結果になっても化けて出やしない。\n重荷を背負わせちまうことになるけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01559",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……分かり、ました。\nそんなことにならないのが一番ですけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01560",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ジョゼさんの気持ちを尊重します。\nただ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01561",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ただ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01562",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "タイニーさんはジョゼさんを受け入れてくれますよ。\n私の友達にも似たような境遇の子がいますから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01563",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "おじいちゃんの命令だったとはいえ、悪事を働き、\n今は、その罪の意識に苦しんでいる子が",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01564",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうか……\nでも、君がいて救われてるんだろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01565",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺はとてもじゃないが、面と向かって彼女とは話せない\n……生き残るために色々やりすぎた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01566",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それじゃあ、また。雷鳴の島で",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01567",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "大したお構いもできずに。\nでは、また！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01568",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ジョゼさん、まだ若いと思うんだけどなぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01569",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]